Introduction

Gyubin is a South Korean singer under LIVEWORKS Company. Described as a 'super rookie,' Gyubin possesses a comprehensive set of musical skills, ranging from captivating vocals to proficiency in guitar, piano, and songwriting.

At sixteen years old, she began her promotions as a pre-debut artist by taking on collaboration project singles, together with accomplished musicians such as Dynamic Duo's Gaeko, Nell, and Wonstein.
